name: Genko Temple
description:
An elk, a wizard, a powerful field, what seems like chaos, will sure help you wield. The apes of the future need far fewer sutures.

Created with an LED fiber optic whip completely unedited long exposure photograph but mirrored to a 8532 x 3900 pixel resolution

Over the years Reid of Harmonic Light has worked for some of his all time favorite companies: Ted, The Grammys, Chan Zuckerberg, Apple, Amazon AWS, Electronic Arts, Robinhood, Cisco, Visa, Adidas, Samsung, MTV, Lighting in a Bottle, Desert Hearts, Lucidity, Sonic Bloom, Northern Nights and more than 80 other festivals.
